                        {
                            "type": "markdown_panel",
                            "key": "query_sources",
                            "data": {
                                "content": "### The two read paths\n\n**Active-record** (`ModelQuery`, hydrates `Ticket` models):\n\n```php\nTicket::query()->where('status', $status)->get();\n```\n\n**Data-mapper** (`QueryBuilder` repository seam, raw rows + aggregate):\n\n```php\nQueryBuilder::on($connection, 'demo_tickets')\n    ->where('status', Operator::EQ, $status)\n    ->count();\n```\n\nBoth hit the single `demo_tickets` SQLite table; the parity table above asserts every status count matches."
                            }
